entry.def: The fortieth item in a series is the one that you count as number forty.

example.ex: It was the fortieth anniversary of the death of the composer.
example.tran: 这是该作曲家逝世 40 周年纪念日。

means.word_mean: 1. position 40 in a countable series of things
1. the ordinal number of forty in counting order
